ray played his last match at Wimbledon earlier this month in a first-round men's doubles defeat alongside his brother Jamie.\", \"from\": 1203, \"to\": 1330, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1205, \"end\": 1211, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.1642347835312415e-31, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 1237, \"end\": 1246, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2013_Wimbledon_Championships\", \"score\": 0.9362142544684946, \"rank\": 0.03921133794965841, \"text\": \"Wimbledon\", \"types\": [\"Q500834\", \"Q1656682\", \"Q13219666\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2013_Wimbledon_Championships\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2013_Wimbledon_Championships\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was forced to withdraw from the singles bya back problem that occurred just a fortnight before the championships while playing at Queen's Club.\", \"from\": 1332, \"to\": 1478, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Scotwas also due to play mixed doubles with Emma Raducanubut his partner pulled out at the 11th hour amid concerns that aggravating a wrist injury could hamper her singles run.\", \"from\": 1480, \"to\": 1660, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1530, \"end\": 1534, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Swan\", \"score\": 0.5981874399342146, \"rank\": 0.6716547453766446, \"text\": \"Emma\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Swan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Swan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Arrived in Paris for my last ever tennis tournament@OlympicsCompeting for \\ud83c\\uddec\\ud83c\\udde7 have been by far the most memorable weeks of my career and I am extremely proud to get do it one final time!pic.twitter.com/keqnpvSEE1  Murrayhas indicated all yearthat this would be his last season on the circuit and saidhe hoped to have one last chance to play the Olympics before retirement.\", \"from\": 1662, \"to\": 2033, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1675, \"end\": 1680, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999997593477, \"rank\": 2.4065774405109163e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Games officially begin on Friday, withthe tennis commencing on Saturday at Roland Garros, home of the French Open.\", \"from\": 2035, \"to\": 2153, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2118, \"end\": 2131, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Open\", \"score\": 0.9999996941826806, \"rank\": 1.4647175456649664e-07, \"text\": \"Roland Garros\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Open\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Open\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Share this article  Subscribe to the City AM newsletter to have our top stories delivered directly to your inbox.\", \"from\": 2155, \"to\": 2268, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow us for breaking news and latest updates\", \"from\": 2270, \"to\": 2316, \"entities\": []}]}"